Smart Ticket Insights App for Splunk

Contributor: Greg Ainslie-Malik, gainsliemalik@splunk.com

The app is designed to provide an automated workflow for training machine learning models to identify frequently occurring types of tickets.

Within the app there is a pipeline on top of the Machine Learning Toolkit that allows users to follow some simple click-and-select steps to load their ticket data and select some important features in the data. The app then decides how it should be processed by an ML algorithm – including automatically deciding how the data should be pre-processed in preparation for an algorithm.

Ultimately the app provides non-expert users identify frequently occuring types of tickets

Prerequesites for this app:
- Splunk Machine Learning Toolkit installed: https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/2890/
- Wordcloud Custom Visualization app installed: https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/3212/
- Circlepack Viz app installed: https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/4574/
